---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About OrgoniteGuide | Orgone Energy Knowledge Base" description="OrgoniteGuide is a free knowledge base dedicated to orgone energy, orgonite, and Wilhelm Reich's research.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">About OrgoniteGuide</h1>
    <div class="prose-content text-[#a1a1aa] space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
      <p>OrgoniteGuide is a free knowledge base dedicated to preserving and sharing information about orgone energy, orgonite, and the pioneering work of Wilhelm Reich.</p>
      <p>Our collection of 53 research articles, tutorials, and primary source documents covers everything from the basics of what orgonite is, to advanced DIY construction guides, to scientific research into bioenergy and orgone field effects.</p>
      <p>This site was created to make rare and scattered orgone research accessible to anyone curious about this field — from complete beginners to experienced practitioners and researchers.</p>
      <p>All content is sourced from publicly available research documents, books, and journals. Nothing on this site constitutes medical advice.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
  .prose-content p { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
</style>
